name: Jenny Fox Flowchart Simulator
description:
The goal of the game is to juggle Ultra Fishbunjin 3000 for as long as possible by repeatedly jumping and attacking.

This is a Slap City fan made game. It was inspired by memes, the Cam's Bodacious Tournament series, and love for the Slap City and it's community. Please check out the game Slap City by Ludosity, it's definitely one of the best platform fighting games out there. All the music is from Slap City, composed by the amazingly skilled Mattias Hakulinen.

This game was made during a personal game jam using Unreal Engine 5.
